precis:
Enactment of the CHARGES FOR SERVICES PROVIDED BY THE OFFICE OF THE
SUPERINTENDENT OF FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS REGULATIONS 2002 which prescribe
the fees to be paid for certain documents or services provided by the
Office of the Superintendent, which now include user fees payable by bank
and insurance holding companies.
